Job Details - L&D; Manager - Retail
L&D; Manager - Retail
Maandag 5 mei 2014
Description
We are currently recruiting for an L&D; Manager to join a diversified local company here in Dubai.You will be solely responsible for the retail side of the business and look after all of their training needs.
This will include Customer Service and Sales.
You need to have the ability to communicate with the business and find apply solutions.For this role you must be familiar with the 70,20,10 concept and be able to apply this theory to any development needs. You need to be Arabic speaking for the role as well as English and have regional experience.}
Job Reference:RJMW015811
Position Type:Permanent
Sector:Human Resources, Retail/Wholesale
Job Duration:n/a
Working Hours:Full-time
Location:Dubai, United Arab Emirates
Salary:£58,000 - £78,000 per year
Contact:Rebecca Morecroft, Contact Code: PO Box 125115, Digby Morgan, Digby Morgan (DIFC) Limited, United Arab Emirates
Phone / Fax:971 (0) 4 401 9196 / 44 (0)20 7495 4474
